{"tid":1712163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣有店舖出賣手足，今朝拉左幾個！","createTime":"2019-11-12T13:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T17:50:01.000Z","uid":49300,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bee8de7048d90acbd3fa687ac20ce069c685d513","tid":1712163,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:34:15.000Z","msg":"我朋友係佢客仔無ac，代po<br />\n<br />\n呢間洗車屋老細係深藍，<br />\n之前荃灣幾次封路拎到佢無生意，佢已經好嬲話要見一個拉一個！我朋友親耳聽到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估唔到今朝有手足入左佢鋪頭換裝，俾佢出賣，仲要交埋cctv俾狗！<br />\n<br />\n呢間洗車屋得佢一個返工，無請人。佢通常凌晨先係道，日頭夜晚都無閘歡迎自出自入。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>地址:荃灣 楊屋道137-143 永華工業大廈地下</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRvFACd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRvFACd.png&h=a970b472&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WEdjRaz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWEdjRaz.png&h=98012822&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dnvRHhf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdnvRHhf.png&h=deb0e73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RenApxx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRenApxx.jpg&h=9425c5ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUrUE5T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUrUE5T.jpg&h=a4cacf1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVKnOZd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVKnOZd.jpg&h=bad86643&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZDjRcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZDjRcz.jpg&h=1338afaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紫色寶馬係佢架車，佢人係道，車就係道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d936eaa8367993ce4449638968eb574714a2e0e","tid":1712163,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77ba468a75b97abf2d933020eb7ce1b10c5581d8","tid":1712163,"uid":212274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:45:52.000Z","msg":"如果佢講既係真感點?"},{"pid":"5a81bf2a1804b297edbaf5eb2eb4ed3b202f093e","tid":1712163,"uid":329466,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"睇樣都似藍屍"},{"pid":"df55ea8eea7993265047f657dcccec2c63f0f97e","tid":1712163,"uid":39010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"咁有無交cctv?<br />\n有就仆街啦"},{"pid":"0d1f0bb7599241dfe502819165550c229bf7d5a4","tid":1712163,"uid":69841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a81bf2a1804b297edbaf5eb2eb4ed3b202f093e","tid":1712163,"uid":329466,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"睇樣都似藍屍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"切爾諾貝爾出世嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731af67cce0d6d0db8f2aaaf28155ff39eb2fdba","tid":1712163,"uid":309935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"推，"},{"pid":"e6a4243764aa8314248e646f21f4944d63cb0962","tid":1712163,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df55ea8eea7993265047f657dcccec2c63f0f97e","tid":1712163,"uid":39010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"咁有無交cctv?<br />\n有就仆街啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:08:44.000Z","msg":"交左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma